orkshop" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Workshop" target="_blank">workshops</a> have found growing <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evidence-based_medicine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evidence-based_medicine" target="_blank">evidence</a> that <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Household" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Household" target="_blank">households</a> are under greater <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pressure" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pressure" target="_blank">pressure</a> and strain as they deal with the consequences of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benefit_concert" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benefit_concert" target="_blank">benefit</a> changes &quot
